  dialogue:
  - 'X: Nerves? Pshhh! I''ve got this in the bag. I''m following the greatest hero
    of all time! Why would I be nervous?'
  - 'Y: Ahah, yeah figures...

    Just, please don''t overwork yourself.

    Especially
    not because of him...'
  - Look, here, since you're so confident. Why don't you walk me through a little
    premise?
  - Say you're on this table right? Real small like, how would you get from here,
    into the cabinet in the kitchen?
